      "x": 40,
      "y": 91,
      "width": 352.0,
      "height": 22.4,
      "text": "1. Context = Props 없이 트리를 관통하여 데이터를 전달한다",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#f59e0b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 0,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "item_2",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 121,
      "width": 392.70000000000005,
      "height": 19.599999999999998,
      "text": "→ createContext → Provider(값 제공) → useContext(값 소비)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#a0a0a0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 0,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "item_3",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 147,
      "width": 223.30000000000004,
      "height": 19.599999999999998,
      "text": "→ 중간 컴포넌트가 Props를 전달하지 않아도 된다",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#a0a0a0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 0,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "item_4",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 173,
      "width": 369.6,
      "height": 19.599999999999998,
      "text": "→ React 19: <Context value={...}> (.Provider 생략)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#a0a0a0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 0,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "item_5",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 199,
      "width": 325.6,
      "height": 22.4,
      "text": "2. useReducer + Context = 전역 상태 관리 패턴",
